"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shiraz")）地區的Nasir AlMolk清真寺

**波斯舞蹈**

[![](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/persian-
dance.jpg)](http://photo.vahidrahmanian.net/2010/10/07/persian-dance/)

伊斯法罕（[Isfahan](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isfahan
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isfahan")）四十柱殿（Chehel Sotoun）的壁畫，描繪波斯舞者在薩非王前起舞

